Bismillah...
A Standalone File, 
how it works:
- first of all, create embeddings through 'from langchain_community.embeddings import HuggingFaceEmbeddings'
- second, create pdf text to chunks 
    'from langchain_community.document_loaders import PyPDFLoader'
    'from langchain.text_splitter import RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter'
- third, create vector store using FAISS 'from langchain_community.vectorstores import FAISS'
- forth, load the vector database.
GUI is use so the user can ask questions.
